thread.title: Cindy
thread.title_full: Bake Me A Wish! reviewed by Cindy

author: Cindy
title: Cindy
text: I purchase two of the coffee cakes and both cakes were delicious. I am currently in Afghanistan and the cakes arrived earlier than expected. I would definitely recommend this company to my friends you are not in the U.S. and need a taste of some home baked goods. Thank you Bake Me a Wish for your cakes satisfied my taste for a home baked cake!!!
